edia-tv/story/273171/grigoris-arnaoytogloy-o-paroysiastis-toy-raid-of-cage|title=\u0393\u03c1\u03b7\u03b3\u03cc\u03c1\u03b7\u03c2 \u0391\u03c1\u03bd\u03b1\u03bf\u03cd\u03c4\u03bf\u03b3\u03bb\u03bf\u03c5: \u039f \u03c0\u03b1\u03c1\u03bf\u03c5\u03c3\u03b9\u03b1\u03c3\u03c4\u03ae\u03c2 \u03c4\u03bf\u03c5 \u00abRaid of Cage\u00bb;|first=Gossip-tv|last=Team|website=Gossip-tv.gr}}</ref>\n| ''Raid the Cage''\n| [[ANT1]]\n| Gregory Arnaoutoglou\n| 2017\n|-\n| {{flag|Hungary}}<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://musorvizio.blog.hu/2017/11/17/tv2_uj_vetelkedo_bezar_a_bazar_game_show_kvizmusor|title=Azt nyerhetsz a TV2 \u00faj vet\u00e9lked\u0151j\u00e9ben, amit fel tudsz markolni|website=m\u0171sorv\u00edzi\u00f3}}</ref>\n| ''Bez\u00e1r a baz\u00e1r!''\n| [[TV2 (Hungary)|TV2]]\n| [[:hu:Till Attila|Attila Till]] and [[Majka (rapper)|Majka]]\n| April 9, 2018 \u2013 present\n|-\n| {{flag|Mexico}}<ref>{{cite web |url=http://eltrece.mx/notas/escapeperfecto/189108/inscribete-para-participar-en-el-nuevo-show-escape-perfecto |title=Archived copy |accessdate=2015-01-13 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150206202127/http://eltrece.mx/notas/escapeperfecto/189108/inscribete-para-participar-en-el-nuevo-show-escape-perfecto |archivedate=2015-02-06 }}</ref>\n| ''Escape perfecto''\n| [[Azteca TV]] \n| Rafael Mercadante and Adianez Hern\u00e1ndez\n| March 2, 2015 \u2013 present\n|-\n| {{flag|Paraguay}}\n| ''Escape perfecto''\n| [[Telefuturo]]\n| Daniel Da Rosa and Lali Gonz\u00e1lez\n| June 14, 2016 \u2013 present\n|-\n| {{flag|Peru}}<ref>[http://www.larepublica.pe/02-10-2014/sully-y-marco-juntos-en-reality-escape-perfecto]</ref>\n| ''Escape perfecto''\n| [[Am\u00e9rica Televisi\u00f3n]] \n| Marco Zunino and Sully S\u00e1enz\n| April 25, 2015 \u2013 present\n|-\n| {{flag|Portugal}}\n| ''Apanha se Puderes''\n| [[Televis\u00e3o Independente|TVI]] \n| [[Cristina Ferreira]] and Pedro Teixeira<br>[[Rita Pereira (actress)|Rita Pereira]] and Pedro Teixeira\n|March 13, 2017 \u2013 August 24, 2019\n|-\n| {{flag|Romania}}<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.libertatea.ro/entertainment/liviu-varciu-deschide-camera-comorilor-video-991908|title=Liviu V\u00e2rciu DESCHIDE CAMERA COMORILOR &#124; VIDEO &#124; Entertainment, Monden|date=February 21, 2014|website=Libertatea}}</ref>\n| ''Deschide camera comorilor''\n| [[Kanal D Romania|Kanal D]]\n| Liviu V\u00e2rciu\n|March 12, 2014 \u2013 July 31, 2017\n|-\n| {{flag|Russia}}<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://russia.tv/brand/show/brand_id/46184/|title=\u041a\u043b\u0435\u0442\u043a\u0430 / \u0422\u0435\u043b\u0435\u043a\u0430\u043d\u0430\u043b \u00ab\u0420\u043e\u0441\u0441\u0438\u044f 1\u00bb|website=russia.tv}}</ref>\n| \u041a\u043b\u0435\u0442\u043a\u0430<br>''Kletka''\n| [[Russia 1]]\n| Dmitry Guberniev\n|August 16, 2014 \u2013 September 27, 2014\n|-\n|{{Flag|Thailand}}\n|''Raid the Cage \u0e1b\u0e23\u0e30\u0e15\u0e39\u0e01\u0e23\u0e07\u0e25\u0e48\u0e32\u0e02\u0e2d\u0e07''\n|[[Channel 7 (Thailand)|Channel 7 HD]]\n|Varavuth Jentanakul and Karnklao Duaysienklao\n| TBA\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" |{{flag|Turkey}}\n| rowspan=\"2\" | ''Kapanmadan Kazan''\n| [[aTV (Turkey)|ATV]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.atv.com.tr/webtv/kapanmadan-kazan/fragman/13?id=34cb736a-6fc3-4afb-9c5c-59e22d97facc|title=Kapanmadan Kazan - 13.B\u00f6l\u00fcm fragman\u0131 - atv|website=www.atv.com.tr}}</ref>\n| Murat Serezli\n|June 17, 2013 \u2013 July 26, 2013\n|-\n| [[Star TV (Turkey)|Star TV]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.startv.com.tr/dizi|title=Dizi izle - T\u00fcm Diziler &#124; Star TV|website=startv.com.tr}}</ref>\n| Alp K\u0131r\u015fan\n| June 5, 2019 \u2013 present\n|-\n| {{flag|Uruguay}}<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.canal10.com.uy/contenidos/escape-perfecto.html|title=Escape Perfecto - Canal 10 el canal uruguayo. Transmisi\u00f3n en vivo 24 h. Programas completos, series, videos, contenidos exclusivos, noticias de Subrayado.|website=canal10.com.uy}}</ref>\n| ''Escape perfecto''<br>''Escape perfecto Famosos''\n| [[Saeta TV Channel 10|